01:18:47.782 --> 01:18:50.952
[man] <i>As the serpent
said unto the woman,</i>

01:18:50.994 --> 01:18:53.412
<i>ye shall not surely die</i>

01:18:53.454 --> 01:18:56.874
<i>for God doth know that in
the day ye eat thereof,</i>

01:18:56.916 --> 01:19:01.921
<i>then your eyes shall be opened,
and ye shall be as gods.</i>

